### Module 03 — rate limiting

@base = http://localhost:3003

### Directory
GET {{base}}/

### Not limited
GET {{base}}/open

### Fixed window: 5 per 10 seconds — click 7 times fast, watch for 429
GET {{base}}/fixed

### Sliding window: 5 per 10 seconds — same limit, no boundary burst
GET {{base}}/sliding

### Per-user (free tier — 10/min)
GET {{base}}/api
x-user-id: u-100
x-tier: free

### Per-user (pro tier — 100/min)
GET {{base}}/api
x-user-id: u-100
x-tier: pro
